headline: Baird Upgrades KeyCorp (KEY) after Decline in Regional Bank Stocks
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) is included among the 14 Best GARP Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On February 24, Baird upgraded KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) to Neutral from Underperform and kept its price target at $19. The firm said the upgrade reflects valuation following the previous day’s selloff.
